@@ -42,3 +42,8 @@ hush wraps a dev command and compresses its output.

 ## Stats

+Run `hush stats` to see how much has been compressed.
+
+The compression ratio per command is tracked in CI and posted to the job
+summary on every push to main, so regressions in compaction are visible.
+
